  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 947c76105d7454747a8fc8874cd8bff8, type: 3}
  m_Name: SM Morning 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - Another day, another dollar. I walk into the office again.
  - This time holding a cup of coffee in hand.
  - The space feels less empty, more lived in. I guess I can attribute that to myself.
  - 'I sit down behind the monitor and log in. '
  - "The time reads \u201C5:00am\u201D. I don\u2019t know why I\u2019m here so early. "
  - 'I guess becoming an exorcist leaves me awake while the rest of the city sleeps. '
  line: 
